EN: Her mother is a homemaker.

ZH: 我母亲认真地教我做人。
EN: My mother taught me how to be a good person.

ZH: 这位母亲对孩子们非常关心。
EN: This mother cares deeply for her children.

ZH: 我的母亲经常给我写信。
EN: My mother writes letters to me often.

ZH: 他母亲今年已经五十岁了。
EN: His mother is fifty years old this year.

ZH: 我母亲是独生子女。
EN: I am an only child of my mother.

